{% extends '::base.html.twig' %}



{% block browser_detection %}{% endblock browser_detection %}

{% block head %}
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
{% endblock head %}
{% block header %} {% endblock header %}
{% block stylesheets %}
	<style type="text/css">
		@font-face {
		    font-family: 'League Gothic';
		    src: url('assets/css/fonts/leaguegothic-regular-webfont.eot');
		    src: url('assets/css/fonts/leaguegothic-regular-webfont.eot?#iefix') format('embedded-opentype'),
		         url('assets/css/fonts/leaguegothic-regular-webfont.woff') format('woff'),
		         url('assets/css/fonts/leaguegothic-regular-webfont.ttf') format('truetype'),
		         url('assets/css/fonts/leaguegothic-regular-webfont.svg#league_gothicregular') format('svg');
		    font-weight: normal;
		    font-style: normal;
		}
		body { margin: 30px 35px; background: black; background-size: 100%; text-align: center; }
		img { display: block; margin: 25px auto; }
		p { color: #fff; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; margin: 25px 0; }
		p.intro { margin: 35px 0 50px; }
		.icons {
			margin: 25px auto;
			vertical-align: middle;
		}
		.icons a {
			display: inline-block;
		}
		.icons img {
			display: inline;
			margin: 0 6px;
			vertical-align: middle;
		}

		.icons img.kut-logo {
			margin: 0 18px;
		}
	</style>
{% endblock stylesheets %}

{% block browser_detection_content %}{% endblock browser_detection_content %}

{% block body %}
	<img src="{{ asset('images/mobile/zeega_logo_mobile.png') }}" alt="zeega-logo" width="160">
	<p class="intro">
	
	The Internet is a wild place. We like that. Too often, though, it’s overwhelming. And full of too many choices.
	<br><br>

	Little by little, we want to help remake the Internet. To make it a more beautiful and surprising place. To make the web’s wilds accessible to anyone for new forms of creative expression.
	<br><br>

	Zeega is revolutionizing web publishing and interactive storytelling for the immersive web. With Zeega, anyone can easily mix media from across the web and share it across networks. Some people have called it a HyperCard for the Internet age. This is a new era, when seamless layering of images, photos, videos, text and timing define digital experiences.
	<br><br>

	For now, Zeega can rock your world on a laptop. We're in the middle of making an awesome mobile experience. Can't wait to share it with y'all soon!</p>
	<div class="icons">
		<a href="http://www.zeega.com">
			<img src="{{ asset('images/mobile/tumblr_logo.png') }}" alt="tumblr-logo" width="23">
		</a>
		<a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Zeega/242930292457056?fref=ts">
			<img src="{{ asset('images/mobile/facebook_logo.png') }}" alt="facebook-logo" width="23">
		</a>
		<a href="https://twitter.com/zeega">
			<img src="{{ asset('images/mobile/twitter_logo.png') }}" alt="twitter-logo" width="23">
		</a>
		
	</div>

{% endblock body %}
{% block footer %} {% endblock footer %}